\fB\-pub \fIoption\fR, \fB\-\-public\-visibility \fIoption\fR
Sets whether the group's status is visible on the public status page.
If this value is changed from the current value, the public status page is regenerated.
The value for \fIoption\fR must be one of \fBtrue\fR, \fBfalse\fR, \fByes\fR, \fBno\fR, \fB1\fR, or \fB0\fR.
Default: 0
